<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:07:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哥伦比亚曾经是以色列人的梦想学校。现在他们成了校园贱民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-used-to-be-a-dream-school-for-israelis-now-theyre-campus-pariahs/0000018f-3dcb-d0b5-a59f-3dcfd8cf0000</link><description>许多人认为，位于美国校园亲巴勒斯坦团结运动最前沿的哥伦比亚大学的加沙抗议活动并不是反犹太主义的。很难声称他们不针对以色列人</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 13:34:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-used-to-be-a-dream-school-for-israelis-now-theyre-campus-pariahs/0000018f-3dcb-d0b5-a59f-3dcfd8cf0000</guid></item><item><title>美国亲巴勒斯坦抗议者正在将 BDS 重新带回加沙。或者他们是吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-pro-palestinian-protesters-are-bringing-bds-back-over-gaza-or-are-they/0000018f-3be3-d414-a5bf-bbf7ec250000</link><description>撤资与以色列-加沙战争有关的公司一直是亲巴勒斯坦抗议者的号角之一，但收效甚微。对星巴克、麦当劳等的抵制影响较小，但远离校园的加沙营地</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:51:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-pro-palestinian-protesters-are-bringing-bds-back-over-gaza-or-are-they/0000018f-3be3-d414-a5bf-bbf7ec250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方任命了一批新的高级指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-appoints-slew-of-new-senior-commanders/0000018f-3d5a-d8f8-abbf-7f5af6bf0000</link><description>任命什洛米·宾德为军事情报局局长预计会因他参与 10 月 7 日大屠杀之前的失败而受到批评</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-appoints-slew-of-new-senior-commanders/0000018f-3d5a-d8f8-abbf-7f5af6bf0000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特因涉嫌在西岸青少年被谋杀后的骚乱中谋杀巴勒斯坦人而逮捕了以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-arrests-israeli-for-murder-of-palestinian-during-riots-after-w-bank-teen-murder/0000018f-3ddb-d8f8-abbf-7fdb7b4d0000</link><description>14 岁定居者本雅明·阿希米尔 (Binyamin Ahimeir) 被谋杀后，定居者在西岸村庄横冲直撞，一名 17 岁巴勒斯坦男孩头部中弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:36:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-arrests-israeli-for-murder-of-palestinian-during-riots-after-w-bank-teen-murder/0000018f-3ddb-d8f8-abbf-7fdb7b4d0000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院检察官：内塔尼亚胡和军队高层面临逮捕令，威胁“破坏”了工作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/icc-prosecutor-work-undermined-by-threats-as-netanyahu-army-brass-face-arrest-warrants/0000018f-3de3-d8f8-abbf-7fe39b8d0000</link><description>周二，内塔尼亚胡称以色列军事和政治官员因在加沙犯下的罪行而受到逮捕令的可能性是“反犹太仇恨犯罪”</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/icc-prosecutor-work-undermined-by-threats-as-netanyahu-army-brass-face-arrest-warrants/0000018f-3de3-d8f8-abbf-7fe39b8d0000</guid></item><item><title>人质交易和拉法攻势达到临界点，以色列可能会崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-and-rafah-op-reach-tipping-point-and-israel-could-fall-either-way/0000018f-3a0e-d0b5-a59f-3bcf9a540000</link><description>人质交易陷入了内塔尼亚胡的“岩石”和辛瓦尔的“困境”之间，全世界都在等待哈马斯对当前提议的答复。彻底的胜利”被认为是</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-and-rafah-op-reach-tipping-point-and-israel-could-fall-either-way/0000018f-3a0e-d0b5-a59f-3bcf9a540000</guid></item><item><title>尽管一再要求，以色列总理办公室仍未提交向哈马斯转移资金的文件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-pms-office-yet-to-submit-files-on-transfer-of-funds-to-hamas-despite-requests/0000018f-3a5f-d8fb-a1df-bf7f5b780000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的局没有遵守国家审计长要求的在 10 月 7 日之前对政府和军队进行调查的文件。总理办公室称这一声明是“战争时期不必要的冲突”，并表示他们已配合所有要求</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-pms-office-yet-to-submit-files-on-transfer-of-funds-to-hamas-despite-requests/0000018f-3a5f-d8fb-a1df-bf7f5b780000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡是不断送给哈马斯及其种族主义联盟伙伴的礼物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-gift-that-keeps-on-giving-to-hamas-and-his-racist-coalition-partners/0000018f-3afb-d414-a5bf-bbff91c40000</link><description>以色列总理的策略很明确：安抚支持其政府的战争贩子，并向哈马斯暗示它不应同意任何协议 ■ 内塔尼亚胡实际上可以从被国际刑事法院宣布为战犯中受益</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-gift-that-keeps-on-giving-to-hamas-and-his-racist-coalition-partners/0000018f-3afb-d414-a5bf-bbff91c40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，据信在加沙被扣为人质的埃利亚基姆·利布曼 (Elyakim Libman) 于 10 月 7 日被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article-live/eight-syrian-soldiers-injured-in-alleged-israeli-strike/0000018f-3c41-d516-afbf-fec39bd90000</link><description>纽约时报：以色列与阿拉伯国家和美国联盟权衡战后加沙计划 ■ 国际刑事法院检察官办公室谴责干涉工作的企图，因为对以色列官员的逮捕令正在审查中 ■ 土耳其表示将停止与以色列的贸易，直到加沙永久停火，援助自由流动 ■ 纽约时报：美国和沙特阿拉伯可能签署正常化协议，以巴勒斯坦国协议为条件调整以色列/沙特关系</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:29:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article-live/eight-syrian-soldiers-injured-in-alleged-israeli-strike/0000018f-3c41-d516-afbf-fec39bd90000</guid></item><item><title>基布兹称，德罗尔·奥尔 (Dror Or) 于 10 月 7 日被杀，据信是加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/dror-or-believed-to-be-among-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-was-killed-on-oct-7-kibbutz-says/0000018f-3bf9-d8f8-abbf-7bf9ff9d0000</link><description>奥尔的妻子被谋杀，他的孩子被扣为人质；他的尸体仍被哈马斯扣押</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/dror-or-believed-to-be-among-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-was-killed-on-oct-7-kibbutz-says/0000018f-3bf9-d8f8-abbf-7bf9ff9d0000</guid></item><item><title>“在玻利维亚做犹太人并不容易。我需要在这里，在以色列”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-03/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-easy-being-a-jew-in-bolivia-i-need-to-be-here-in-israel/0000018f-3af7-d414-a5bf-bbf798a80000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名犹太裔玻利维亚人思考自 70 年代居住在这里以来以色列发生的变化，一名俄罗斯移民解释了他离开圣彼得堡前往特拉维夫的原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-03/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-easy-being-a-jew-in-bolivia-i-need-to-be-here-in-israel/0000018f-3af7-d414-a5bf-bbf798a80000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯外交官称埃及试图说服哈马斯在达成协议后不要重启战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/arab-diplomats-say-egypt-trying-to-convince-hamas-not-to-restart-war-after-deal/0000018f-3ae6-d17f-adcf-fbe75dee0000</link><description>外交官们证实了黎巴嫩的一份报告，称埃及的提议不包括以色列不返回加沙地带的详细承诺，埃及正试图说服哈马斯，该提议将保证该激进组织的安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/arab-diplomats-say-egypt-trying-to-convince-hamas-not-to-restart-war-after-deal/0000018f-3ae6-d17f-adcf-fbe75dee0000</guid></item><item><title>被任命的以色列警察局长与一名被定罪的诈骗犯之间的密谋对话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiring-conversation-between-the-appointed-police-chief-and-a-convicted-fraudster/0000018f-3a7b-d516-afbf-fefb5ade0000</link><description>2015 年，本·格维尔 (Ben Gvir) 挑选的警察局长阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德 (Avshalom Peled) 在电话中请求他的朋友摩西·达顿 (Moshe Dadon) 帮助掩盖他家中的建筑违规行为。他不知道的是，国家反欺诈部门正在监听这个电话，调查达东。通话记录已经公布</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:23:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiring-conversation-between-the-appointed-police-chief-and-a-convicted-fraudster/0000018f-3a7b-d516-afbf-fefb5ade0000</guid></item><item><title>卢旺达种族灭绝？布隆迪大屠杀？以色列一切如常</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/genocide-in-rwanda-massacre-in-burundi-its-business-as-usual-for-israel/0000018f-3ad3-d414-a5bf-bbf752870000</link><description>胡图族在卢旺达屠杀数十万图西族的二十年前，图西族在布隆迪屠杀了胡图族。有关以色列向卢旺达提供军事援助的记录仍然是绝密，但解密的外交部有关布隆迪的信件暗示对种族屠杀漠不关心</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:18:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/genocide-in-rwanda-massacre-in-burundi-its-business-as-usual-for-israel/0000018f-3ad3-d414-a5bf-bbf752870000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫描绘了加沙儿童的痛苦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-paints-the-pain-of-gazan-children/0000018f-39b7-d516-afbf-fff725ce0000</link><description>《纯真被破坏：战时的儿童》拒绝对加沙的死亡和破坏视而不见，以色列纪录片周 DocAviv 和耶路撒冷作家节将于本月晚些时候回归</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:06:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-paints-the-pain-of-gazan-children/0000018f-39b7-d516-afbf-fff725ce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙拉法的入侵将是致命的。有一个更好的办法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-02/ty-article/.highlight/an-israeli-invasion-of-gazas-rafah-will-be-deadly-there-is-a-better-way/0000018f-3a04-d9c3-abcf-7a75d7af0000</link><description>拆除拉法隧道是以色列-加沙边境长期安全的关键要求。但在做出攻击加沙南部城市的重大决定之前，以色列必须仔细研究这一替代方案</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 19:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-02/ty-article/.highlight/an-israeli-invasion-of-gazas-rafah-will-be-deadly-there-is-a-better-way/0000018f-3a04-d9c3-abcf-7a75d7af0000</guid></item><item><title>解救人质的内塔尼亚胡兄弟的私人信件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-private-letters-of-the-netanyahu-brother-who-did-rescue-hostages/0000018f-3a62-d9c3-abcf-7a77a6f00000</link><description>重读 1976 年在恩德培英勇牺牲的约尼·内塔尼亚胡 (Yoni Netanyahu) 的信件，可能会揭示他弟弟本杰明 (Benjamin) 令人不安的性格。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 19:39:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-private-letters-of-the-netanyahu-brother-who-did-rescue-hostages/0000018f-3a62-d9c3-abcf-7a77a6f00000</guid></item><item><title>自战争开始以来，西岸整个地区的社区已被清空</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-war-began-entire-areas-of-the-west-bank-have-been-emptied-of-their-communities/0000018f-39a9-d9c3-abcf-7bfd66980000</link><description>10 月 7 日，约旦河西岸的定居者暴力达到了顶峰：自此，18 个巴勒斯坦牧民社区被迫背井离乡，居民现在住在其他村庄郊区的临时住所里，一贫如洗，对未来感到焦虑</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 19:33:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-war-began-entire-areas-of-the-west-bank-have-been-emptied-of-their-communities/0000018f-39a9-d9c3-abcf-7bfd66980000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，土耳其在加沙战争期间停止了与以色列的所有贸易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/turkey-reportedly-halts-all-trade-with-israel-amid-war-in-gaza/0000018f-3a77-d9c3-abcf-7a770e3a0000</link><description>土耳其尚未正式宣布此举，正值加沙战争期间两国关系紧张，但以色列进口商已经抱怨发货延迟</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 18:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/turkey-reportedly-halts-all-trade-with-israel-amid-war-in-gaza/0000018f-3a77-d9c3-abcf-7a770e3a0000</guid></item><item><title>反以色列校园活动人士不是纳粹分子。但他们是特朗普法西斯主义的同谋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-campus-activists-arent-nazis-but-theyre-complicit-with-trumps-fascism/0000018f-39c6-d8fb-a1df-bde68ff70000</link><description>当内塔尼亚胡可笑地将亲巴勒斯坦学生与纳粹进行比较时，他只是让极少数享有特权的少数人更容易坚持认为他们不是真正的反犹太主义者，而只是“反犹太复国主义者”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 18:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-campus-activists-arent-nazis-but-theyre-complicit-with-trumps-fascism/0000018f-39c6-d8fb-a1df-bde68ff70000</guid></item></channel></rss>